\c 9
\p
\v 1 Rega kufara, iwe Israeri, kuve mufaro, semarudzi; nokuti iwe wakafeva uchibva kuna Mwari wako; wakada mubairo wechifeve pamaburiro ese ezviyo.
\v 2 Buriro nechisviniro chewaini hazvingavapi zvekudya, uye waini itsva ichavanyengera.
\v 3 Havangagari munyika yaJehovha; asi Efuremu achadzokera kuEgipita, uye vachadya zvisina kuchena paAsiriya.
\v 4 Havangadiriri waini kuna Jehovha, uye havangamufadzi; zvibairo zvavo zvichava sechingwa chemariro kwavari; vese vanodya pachiri vachasvibiswa, nokuti chingwa chavo chemweya wavo hachingasviki muimba yaJehovha.
\v 5 Muchaitei nezuva remutambo wakatarwa, nepazuva remabiko aJehovha?
\v 6 Nokuti tarirai, vakaenda nekuda kwekuparadza. Egipita richavaunganidza, Memifisi achavaviga; \add nzvimbo\add* dzinofadza dzesirivha yavo, rukato rwuchadzigara nhaka, minzwa ichava mumatende avo.
\p
\v 7 Mazuva ekushanyirwa asvika, mazuva ekutsiva asvika; Israeri achaziva; muporofita ibenzi, munhu wemweya anopenga, nekuda kweuwandu hweuipi hwenyu, neruvengo rukuru.
\v 8 Efuremu mushori kuna Mwari wangu; \add asi\add* muporofita, rugombe rwemuteyi weshiri ruri munzira dzake dzose, ruvengo mumba yaMwari wake.
\v 9 Vaka\add zvi\add*odza zvakadzama, sepamazuva eGibhiya; acharangarira uipi hwavo, achashanyira zvivi zvavo.
\v 10 Ndakawana Israeri vakaita semazambiringa murenje; ndakaona madzibaba enyu vakaita sechibereko chekutanga pamuonde pakutanga kwacho; \add asi\add* ivo vakaenda kuBhaari-Peori, vakazviparadzanisira kune zvinyadzo, vakava zvinyangadzo sepamadiro avo.
\v 11 \add Kana ari\add* Efuremu, rukudzo rwavo rwuchabhururuka seshiri, kubva pakubereka, uye kubva muchizvaro, uye kubva pakubata mimba.
\v 12 Kunyange vakarera vana vavo, zvakadaro ndichavaita vafirwe, kusa\add sara\add* nemunhu. Zvirokwazvo, nhamowo kwavari pakubva kwangu kwavari.
\v 13 Efuremu, sekuona kwangu Tire, wakasimwa panzvimbo yekugara, asi Efuremu achabudisira vana vake kumuurayi.
\v 14 Vapei, Jehovha, muchapei? Vapei chizvaro chinosvosva, nemazamu akaoma.
\v 15 Uipi hwavo hwese huri paGirigari, nokuti ndipo ndakavavenga; nekuda kweuipi hwezviito zvavo, ndichavadzinga kubuda mumba mangu; handichazovadizve; machinda avo ese vapanduki.
\v 16 Efuremu warohwa; mudzi wavo waoma; havangazobereki chibereko; hongu, kunyange vakabereka zvakadaro ndichauraya vadikanwi vechizvaro chavo.
\v 17 Mwari wangu achavaramba, nokuti havana kumuteerera; uye vachava vadzungairi pakati pevechirudzi.